OL,3,CIran rejects Trump's foul-mouthed
OL,4,Cdemand to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIranian armed forces have declared the
OL,7,FStrait of Hormuz will "never return to
OL,8,Fits former state, especially for
OL,9,FAmerica and Israel" after US President
OL,10,FDonald Trump launched a foul-mouthed
OL,11,Ftirade about the waterway.
OL,13,FThe president demanded on Sunday that
OL,14,FIran reopen the passage way and warned
OL,15,Fthe regime would be "living in hell"
OL,16,Fif it did not happen before a new
OL,17,Fdeadline of Tuesday 8pm ET.
OL,19,F"Tuesday will be Power Plant Day, and
OL,20,FBridge Day, all wrapped up in one, in
OL,21,FIran," Trump said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
