OL,3,CIran rejects Trump's foul-mouthed
OL,4,Cdemand to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,F"There will be nothing like it!!! Open
OL,7,Fthe F***in' Strait, you crazy
OL,8,Fbastards, or you'll be living in Hell
OL,9,F- JUST WATCH! Praise be to Allah."
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps
OL,17,FNavy responded to Trump with a post on
OL,18,FX: "The Strait of Hormuz will never
OL,19,Freturn to its former state, especially
OL,20,Ffor America and Israel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
