OL,3,CIran rejects Trump's foul-mouthed
OL,4,Cdemand to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,F"The Navy of the IRGC is in the
OL,7,Fprocess of completing the operational
OL,8,Fpreparations for the announced plan of
OL,9,FIran's officials for the new order in
OL,10,Fthe Persian Gulf."
OL,12,FThe conflict has now entered its sixth
OL,13,Fweek, and overnight strikes on cities
OL,14,Facross Iran killed more than 25
OL,15,Fpeople, with reports of children among
OL,16,Fthe dead.
