OL,3,CIran rejects Trump's foul-mouthed
OL,4,Cdemand to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIranian attacks injured four people in
OL,7,Fthe Haifa, Israel, early Monday and a
OL,8,FGhanaian man suffered wounds from
OL,9,Fshrapnel in Abu Dhabi, after the
OL,10,Finterception of an Iranian missile,
OL,11,FUAE authorities said.
OL,13,FUS issues Iran new deadline
OL,15,FTrump has threatened to attack Iran's
OL,16,Fpower plants and bridges if the Strait
OL,17,Fof Hormuz is not reopened by Tuesday
OL,18,F8pm ET (1am BST).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
