OL,3,CIran rejects Trump's foul-mouthed
OL,4,Cdemand to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIt is not the first time Trump has set
OL,7,Fa deadline for Iran to reopen the
OL,8,Fstrait - an essential waterway through
OL,9,Fwhich a fifth of the world's oil
OL,10,Fpasses - with the president extending
OL,11,Fthe time limit each time before it
OL,12,Fruns out.
OL,14,FThe previous deadline was set for
OL,15,FApril 6, after which Trump said the US
OL,16,Fwould strike Iranian energy
OL,17,Finfrastructure.
OL,19,FTrump will hold a news conference with
OL,20,Fthe military at 1pm ET (5pm ET) on
OL,21,FMonday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
