OL,3,CIran rejects Trump's foul-mouthed
OL,4,Cdemand to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThe Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps
OL,7,FNavy have declared that the Strait of
OL,8,FHormuz will "never return to its
OL,9,Fformer state, especially for America
OL,10,Fand Israel".
OL,12,FStrikes across Iran kill more than 25
OL,13,Fpeople
OL,15,FAirstrikes across Iran took place
OL,16,FSunday into Monday, with an attack on
OL,17,FEslamshar, southwest of Tehran,
OL,18,Fkilling at least 13 people according
OL,19,Fto the semiofficial Fars news agency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
