OL,3,CIran rejects Trump's foul-mouthed
OL,4,Cdemand to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FFive people were also killed when a
OL,7,Fresidential area in the city of Qom
OL,8,Fwas hit, and six more died in strikes
OL,9,Fon other cities, the state-run IRAN
OL,10,Fdaily newspaper said.
OL,12,FThree people died in Tehran after an
OL,13,Fairstrike hit their home, Iranian
OL,14,Fstate television reported, with
OL,15,Fexplosions and low-flying jets heard
OL,16,Fover the capital for hours overnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
