OL,3,CIran rejects Trump's foul-mouthed
OL,4,Cdemand to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FTehran's Sharif University of
OL,7,FTechnology was also hit, with reports
OL,8,Fof damage to the buildings as well as
OL,9,Fa natural gas distribution site next
OL,10,Fto the campus.
OL,12,FNo students are currently using the
OL,13,Fcampus, as the war has forced all
OL,14,Fclasses online.
OL,16,FIran attacks Israel and Gulf neighbours
