OL,3,CIran rejects Trump's foul-mouthed
OL,4,Cdemand to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIsrael's Magen David Adom and Fire and
OL,7,FRescue services said early Monday that
OL,8,Fthere are several reported sites of
OL,9,FIranian missile hits in the northern
OL,10,Fcity of Haifa.
OL,12,FIn one site, four people were slightly
OL,13,Finjured, including two children.
OL,15,FIt comes one day after another attack
OL,16,Ffrom Iran also hit a Haifa residential
OL,17,Farea on Sunday, killing two people and
OL,18,Finjuring others.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
