OL,3,CIran rejects Trump's foul-mouthed
OL,4,Cdemand to reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIsraeli security forces and rescue
OL,7,Fteams have been working to find people
OL,8,Ftrapped beneath the rubble.
OL,10,FIn the United Arab Emirates' capital
OL,11,Fof Abu Dhabi, authorities said a
OL,12,FGhanaian man had suffered wounds from
OL,13,Fshrapnel after the interception of an
OL,14,FIranian missile over the city's
OL,15,FMusaffah neighborhood.
OL,17,FThe site is near the Al Dhafra Air
OL,18,FBase, which hosts US forces and has
OL,19,Fbeen repeatedly targeted by Iran in
OL,20,Fthe war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
